to investigate the singular equal-mass limit of the\nprecession-averaged expressions, where we find an approximate scaling of $1/(1\n- q)$ with the mass ratio $q$.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 25 Jul 2021 22:26:28 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 18 Jun 2022 20:19:00 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-07-13"}
