er of a signed bipartite planar simple graph on $n$\nvertices. We then show that each of the bounds is tight for any value of $n\\geq\n4$.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 26 Jul 2021 11:50:51 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-07-27"}
